charges.charge_description: 8:1326(a)(b)(1): Illegal Alien Found in the United States Following Deportation(1)

charges.charge_disposition: Defendant is committed to the custody of Bureau of Prisons for 12 months and 1 days. Supervised release for 1 year under the terms and conditions of US Probation Office and General Order 318 or 05-02, including, but not limited to, the condition that defendant shall not commit another federal, state or local crime. Special assessment of 100. All fines are waived
